trans-unit.source: Represents an item in the XQuery 1.0 and XPath 2.0 Data Model.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et element i XQuery 1.0 og XPath 2.0 datamodellen.

trans-unit.source: An item is either a node or an atomic value.
trans-unit.target: Et element er en node eller en atomic-verdi.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called by derived class constructors to initialize state in this type.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kalles av utledede klassen brukes til å initialisere tilstand i denne typen.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value indicating whether the item represents an XPath node or an atomic value.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter en verdi som angir om elementet representerer en XPath-node eller en atomic-verdi.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item represents an XPath node; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the item represents an atomic value.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet representerer en XPath-noden. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis elementet representerer en atomic-verdi.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the current item as a boxed object of the most appropriate [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)] type according to its schema type.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter gjeldende element som et boks objekt av den mest aktuelle [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)] typen i henhold til filtypen skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the item is not valid according to its specified schema type, the value of the TypedValue property is equivalent to the value of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for elementet ikke er gyldig i henhold til den angitte skjematypen, verdien for egenskapen TypedValue tilsvarer verdien for den <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, the ValueType property gets the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] type of the typed value of the item.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, egenskapen verditype henter den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] verditypen typeangitt for elementet.

trans-unit.source: For example, an element of type `xs:int` would have a ValueType of <xref:System.Int32> by default.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel et element av typen `xs:int` må en verditype for <xref:System.Int32>som standard.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: However, the ValueType could be any one of the valid types that can be mapped to `xs:int`, such as <xref:System.Int16> or <xref:System.Double>.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid verditype kan være en av de gyldige typene som kan tilordnes til `xs:int`, for eksempel <xref:System.Int16>eller <xref:System.Double>.</xref:System.Double> </xref:System.Int16>
